title: What Do Artists Do All Day - Dennis Morris - Sno

What Do Artist Do All Day ? - Dennis Morris - Sno

Profile of photographer Dennis Morris, to coincide with an exhibition of his work with Public Image Limited opening at the Institute of Contemporary Arts. The film follows Morris as he works on a photoshoot of punk band Skinny Girl Diet. He reflects on the highlights of his past career, which included documenting the punk scene and London's black community in the 1960s and 1970s, as well as capturing images of Bob Marley and the Sex Pistols on tour.
